er Intake','Taweelah Asia Power Company/Fisia Italimpianti/Arabian Construction Company (ACC)','29 May 2006 - 05 September 2006','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"This project involved the installation of 3 seawater intake pipes including the design of concrete anchor blocks, for the Power and Desalination Plant\'s New \'B\' Extension in Taweelah, UAE. Since the construction had to be carried out in the existing basin of the desalination plant, maintaining the water quality of the basin was a major concern. To prevent the pollution of the nearby water in the basin, a double-layer silt curtain was designed and installed to enclose the works area. To further minimize the disturbance to the existing basin, it was proposed to precast the concrete anchor blocks on site. By making use of the buoyancy force, they were lifted and installed underwater by a 500-ton mobile hydraulic crane sitting on temporary steel H-piles driven near the edge of the temporary cut slope. Subsequent intake pipes were installed underwater by divers. The double layer silt curtain proved to be very effective in preventing the deterioration of water quality during the course of construction.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]','2025-06-01 04:05:12.856000','2025-06-06 08:19:32.489000',NULL,8,3,'en'),(91,'qvqh2cvtmycadw6q26l128oq',' Taweelah發電及海水化淡廠二期擴建海水吸管建造工程','Taweelah發電及海水化淡廠二期擴建海水吸管建造工程','Taweelah Asia Power Company/Fisia Italimpianti/Arabian Construction Company (ACC)','2006 年 05 月 29 日 - 2006 年 09 月 05 日','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"工程包括爲阿聯酋 Taweelah發電及海水化淡廠二期擴建專案安裝三條海水吸管及其水泥塊之設計。因爲工程於現有海水化淡廠裏進行，維持港內海水品質是非常重視。爲了港內海水不受污染，我們設計及安裝了一套雙層隔泥屏障，在水下挖掘及疏浚工程前將整個工程範圍隔開。在整個海水吸管安裝工作過程中，證實了我們設計的雙層防泥膜能有效地防止工程對港內海水品質的影響。\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"在製造水下海水吸管固定塊體方面，我們亦採用了預製方法，來進一步減少對港內海水品質的影響。每一個海水吸管固定塊體重量超過九十公噸，我們利用了海水浮力，潛水員及五百噸吊機來成功完成其水下安裝工作。\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]','2025-06-01 04:06:13.943000','2025-06-01 04:06:13