d construction of pavement at the quay area.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]','2025-06-01 03:55:41.924000','2025-06-06 08:21:09.328000','2025-06-06 08:21:09.377000',8,3,'en'),(245,'lg1n14o9w8q42i94pticuyrn','Management and Capping of Contaminated Mud Pit IV at East of Sha Chau – Phase III (Contract No. CV/2004/06)','Management and Capping of Contaminated Mud Pit IV at East of Sha Chau – Phase III','Civil Engineering and Development Department','02 August 2004 - 01 September 2007','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The project includes capping of Mud Pit IVA and IVB and existing channels with excavated suitable materials; collection and deposition of excavated suitable materials from public filling barging transfer points and management of Sha Chau East\'s disposal facilities.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]','2025-06-01 05:33:17.999000','2025-06-06 08:21:21.091000','2025-06-06 08:21:21.153000',8,3,'en'),(246,'auflehl41lm6iywlbw4xtbvg','Marasy Development - Quay Wall Construction Completion and Maintenance Package','Marasy Development - Quay Wall Construction Completion and Maintenance Package','International Capital Trading L.L.C.','26 January 2009 - 26 December 2009','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The project includes the construction of approximately 780m and 60m long mass concrete blockwork quay walls at Block 99 and 101 respectively;\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"dredging and excavation of the wall foundation, casting and placing of approx. 2,600 pieces of mass concrete blocks to form the quay wall, and placement of fill material.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]','2025-06-01 03:40:11.998000','2025-06-06 08:21:37.654000','2025-06-06 08:21:37.766000',8,3,'en'),(247,'b50cndfrvokkonli5c3l4f6n','Package Contract No. C84-0032 AOS Revitalization - Supply, Installation, Testing and Commissioning of Demolition and Re-Construction of Decking Package Contract','Package Contract No. C84-0032 AOS Revitalization - Supply, Installation, Testing and Commissioning of Demolition and Re-Construction of Decking Package Contract','New World Construction Company Limited','17 December 2015 - 16 September 2018','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The revitalization plan of Avenue of Stars (AOS) was announced in 2015 and the avenue was reopened in 2019.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The reconstruction of the deck structure along the avenue was one of the package contracts of the AOS revitalization project. The works include the demolition and reconstruction of the existing AOS deck structure, the reparation of existing crossheads and the installation of precast cladding panels. It also involves the demolition and reconstruction of the existing connecting bridge from AOS to Hotel InterContinental Hong Kong.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"The AOS project was carried out under the spot lights of mass media. The major challenge facing by the project team is the short contract period. With an ambitious project timeframe, the demolition and reconstruction of around 400m long concrete bridge structure in marine condition is completed within 11 months. The project team is proud to successfully complete the project with high standard of project management in terms of public relation, quality assurance, programme monitoring, budget control, safety and environmental.\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}]','2025-06-01 02:48:39.570000','2025-06-06 08:21:51.229000','2025-06-06 08:21:51.284000',8,3,'en'),(248,'vfb0y556v65526ki0tg3wbm3','Pak Shek Kok Reclamation for Public Filling, Stage III (Contract No. CV/98/01)','Pak Shek Kok Reclamation for Public Filling, Stage III','Civil Engineering Department','30 December 1998 - 17 May 2002','[{\"type\": \"paragraph\", \"children\": [{\"text\": \"Works involved:\", \"type\": \"text\"}]}, {\"type\": \"list\", \"format\": \"unordered\", \"c